{
  "stem": "10960.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She went in ghetto in Dubno.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And although she had a [INAUDIBLE], when they surrounded, and throwed out everybody to the trucks, where they will be killed, my sister was showing her [INAUDIBLE], because this same of one of the drivers came to our house.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He knew Yitzhak.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He knew my brother-in-law.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he told them, he said, I saw the way she was begging.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I have my [INAUDIBLE], and-- and-- and my husband is so-and-so.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Didn't helped.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They just killed her, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The same [INAUDIBLE], like all the Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When I heard that, when I heard that, you know, bombing, and they used to bomb in, throw in grenades in [INAUDIBLE], and the other goyim, and even the Jews who went to work, the men who went to work, they had to cover them with the remaining mud.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But they couldn't cover them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They couldn't kill-- they didn't kill them to death.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They kill them they shall suffer before they were dying.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because people went to next day, within, or whatever, the goyim came, when they told her, they're still alive.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the mud was-- was bubbling up, because they probably were trying to get out from there, from those graves.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The same-- the same moment I said to-- to my brother-in-law, to Yitzhak, you take Gershon with you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I have a little baby.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In case what we will be killed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Gershon will be killed, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the only-- the only way to try go back to that place there, he used to do business with the main-- main man in Dubno.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he end up [NON-ENGLISH] You know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How do we say [INAUDIBLE]?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had his own farm.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His own farm.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He used to do business with the grain business.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
